{
  "stem": "7414.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I told before, that I went to a Polish high school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But by the time I joined the organization Hashomer Hatzair, I started to lose interest in my friends, which I had before, because they, you see, as we grew older, the girls, they started to have interest in dresses and boys and that, which my mind went into a different direction.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very serious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were trying to solve the ills of the whole world then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So [LAUGHS] so I was not interested in gossips with the other girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so when I was in the fifth grade, I decided to switch schools and go to the Jewish school, the Jewish high school, where all my friends from all different groups of Zionist movements were.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And where we learned Hebrew, which I knew a little bit before, because we studied Hebrew in our organization as well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, but we had Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had all the subject, subjects like literature, Jewish, and Hebrew, and Talmud, and everything else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, the normal subjects as every normal public school in Poland had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very happy there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had all the Jewish teachers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As it was quite a small town, we knew each other from home and from before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some were even friends of my eldest siblings, brother and sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was-- first of all, it was a very high standard school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to keep a high standard, to keep the permission to have a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So and I finished there, having those two exams, one for the Hebrew and one for the-- all the other subjects.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I finished very well, with very high degrees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was ready to, to go on my way to university.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
